{"tid":2030853,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府交代海洋公園3項貸款涉中銀　最大筆逾26億元","createTime":"2020-05-23T04:44:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T04:58:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"81121d2c3de3169f04aea6f9c51cdf08b9c9393d","tid":2030853,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1527879_1_L_20200523123605.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1527879_1_L_20200523123605.jpg&h=a7aaf2eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當局交代，海洋公園目前有 3筆商業貸款金額，都涉及中國銀行，3筆貸款的最後還款期均是2020/21年度，政府沒有作擔保。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊事務專員就海洋公園債務情況回覆議員查詢。最大筆涉及中國銀行的商業貸款，涉及海洋公園2005年的重新發展計劃，涉款26億3800萬元，2015/16年度起已償還11億6800萬元，利息及其他財務開支2億7300萬元。<br />\n<br />\n另外，當局披露，涉及海洋公園大樹灣發展項目商業貸款金額達6億5000萬元，另有10億元的商業循環信貸，以應付園方短期營運現金。該兩筆貸款都未開始償還本金。其中就大樹灣項目，園方已償還的利息及其他財務費用，合共1300萬元。"},{"pid":"e78eba2bfeaae84c563b15103b6720bf145ee202","tid":2030853,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dRYfUs9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdRYfUs9.jpg&h=bc3bf07c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a66cbe10cb626561314ba64b28b5d2a7d8b9eca6","tid":2030853,"uid":151469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:47:21.000Z","msg":"dls"},{"pid":"96aea81529fef5c7891c9e3fdc9c8b4c35ace5bd","tid":2030853,"uid":188035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:48:19.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得死都要送錢比威威師令"},{"pid":"b36e82e7783b778e18525841e25141e05550550f","tid":2030853,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}